{"tid":1557882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[薄扶林大學]  光復港大 HKU罷課人鏈咆哮連儂牆行動GROUP上線啦","createTime":"2019-09-10T09:39:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T11:05:05.000Z","uid":302331,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7838940631939dae410e5642001536896372ad0e","tid":1557882,"uid":302331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:39:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">見到暴大開學霸課習會極有霸氣，薄大仔又點可以唔做野呢？！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n星期一見到同學們組成人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />琴日仲有藝術家係USTREET噴字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日經過連儂牆都會見到有個街坊伯伯好有心咁貼文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一轉堂叫口號好開心有手足應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有A2出口成日都有同學著GEAR 拎住文宣（睇到你地對眼好有正氣，一定係靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LViVSxh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLViVSxh.jpg&h=a83b9cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">暫時活動整合</span></strong>：(from <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1551712/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1551712/page/1</a>)<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n每日十二點佔領大學街<br />\n每日轉堂咆哮</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJnSUMB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJnSUMB.jpg&h=9e6b7999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小妹自問係無膽匪類唔敢上前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都想爲港大同香港出一分力，所以決定開TG公海方便各位港大手足討論有咩可以做/搞活動/CALL馬屌走撕紙狗/求物資等等。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公海TG: </span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkuunitedforfivedemands\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkuunitedforfivedemands&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ